<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/55351928" target="_blank" data-id="14360741" data-za-element-name="Title">
为什么JS程序员习惯传入一个对象来作为配置，而非直接传入参数？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/55351928/answer/144167411">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="53197605">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="144167411"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>116</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
<button class="up ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="count">116</span>
<span class="label sr-only">赞同</span>
