<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/31316032" target="_blank" data-id="4723744" data-za-element-name="Title">
Hybrid架构下，加载本地H5资源后，如何处理Ajax请求？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/31316032/answer/75236718">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="25518255">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="75236718"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>113</a>
