<textarea hidden class="content">欢迎加入FreeCodeCamp&lt;br&gt;官网：&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.freecodecamp.com&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;Learn to Code and Help Nonprofits&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;中文网：&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.freecodecamp.cn/&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;Learn to Code and Help Nonprofits&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;有关JS的实践项目有：&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;初级&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.freecodecamp.cn/challenges/design-a-danmu-app&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;Design a danmu app&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 创建一个简单的弹幕发射应用&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;中级&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.freecodecamp.cn/challenges/build-a-random-quote-machine&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;Build a Random Quote Machine&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 随机格言小部件&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.freecodecamp.cn/challenges/show-the-local-weather&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;Show the Local Weather&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 天气预报应用&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.freecodecamp.cn/challenges/build-a-wikipedia-viewer&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;Build a Wikipedia Viewer&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 维基百科查看器&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.co