<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/41212868" target="_blank" data-id="8692449" data-za-element-name="Title">
半路出家前端，投了很多简历都被拒，问题出在哪里？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/41212868/answer/90061811">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="31461248">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="90061811"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>112</a>
</div>

