</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text expandable js-collapse-body" data-resourceid="6754290" data-action="/answer/content" data-author-name="Milo Yip" data-entry-url="/question/36367846/answer/139222110">

<textarea hidden class="content">如果未学过计算机图形学，可试&lt;br&gt;《Interactive 3D Graphics Course with Three.js and WebGL》免费线上课程。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.udacity.com/course/interactive-3d-graphics--cs291&quot; class=&quot; external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://www.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;visible&quot;&gt;udacity.com/course/inte&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;ractive-3d-graphics--cs291&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</textarea>


<div class="zh-summary summary clearfix">

如果未学过计算机图形学，可试 《Interactive 3D Graphics Course with Three.js and WebGL》免费线上课程。 <a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.udacity.com/course/interactive-3d-graphics--cs291" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span class="invisible">https://www.</span><span class="visible">udacity.com/course/inte</span><span class="invisible">ractive-3d-graphics--cs291</span><span class="ellipsis"></span><i class="icon-external"></i></a>

